    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "It is also happening in Chrome. The `select` element seems to have a bit of extra padding (5px). A reduction of 3px seems to work in Firefox and Chrome:\n\n![screenshot from 2015-02-11 21 06 38](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/599274/6161132/0a5a8686-b232-11e4-8e58-557b9a21c49a.png)\n\n![screenshot from 2015-02-11 21 09 01](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/599274/6161145/3b67557e-b232-11e4-99b6-7937022b7439.png)\n\nBy the way, there are a lot styles being overridden in that section of the page and mixing pixels with ems is going to cause some issues.\n"
